luks-enroll (0.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * GTK4/libadwaita wizard for LUKS FIDO2, TPM2, and recovery key enrollment.
  * PIN support for both FIDO2 and TPM2 enrollment.
  * Automatic password keyslot removal after enrollment.

